gql_alloc with GQL_VALUE_LIST; payload is a List of value records.
@End Implementation
@Performance_Hints
O(1).
@End Performance_Hints
@Security_Scope
Owns list.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "gql_value_list" takes values_list as Integer returns Integer:
    Return proc gql_alloc with GQL_VALUE_LIST, values_list, 0, 0, 0
End Process

@Reasoning
Object value (spec section 2.9.9): a list of object-field records, each
