@End Reasoning
@Implementation
gql_alloc with GQL_VALUE_OBJECT; payload is a List of object-field pairs.
@End Implementation
@Performance_Hints
O(1).
@End Performance_Hints
@Security_Scope
Owns list.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "gql_value_object" takes object_fields as Integer returns Integer:
    Return proc gql_alloc with GQL_VALUE_OBJECT, object_fields, 0, 0, 0
End Process

@Reasoning
Variable used as a value (spec section 2.9 + 2.10).
@End Reasoning
