@Security_Scope
Owns all referenced lists and strings.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "gql_object_definition" takes name as Integer, fields as Integer, interfaces as Integer, description as Integer returns Integer:
    Return proc gql_alloc with GQL_TYPE_DEFINITION_OBJECT, name, fields, interfaces, description
